Description:
  Generate a Twitter Bootstrap project with LESS

Example:
  yeoman init bootstrap-less

  This will create:
    .
    |-- app
    |   |-- components
    |   |   |-- backbone
    |   |   |-- bootstrap
    |   |   |-- jquery
    |   |   |-- require-jade
    |   |   |-- requirejs
    |   |   |-- underscore
    |   |
    |   |-- images
    |   |
    |   |-- javascripts
    |   |   |-- collections
    |   |   |-- models
    |   |   |-- templates
    |   |   |-- views
    |   |   |-- app.js
    |   |   |-- main.js
    |   |
    |   |-- less
    |   |   |-- customization
    |   |   |   |-- // bootstrap overrides
    |   |   |   |-- ...
    |   |   |
    |   |   |-- app.less
    |   |   |-- bootstrap.less // @import bootstrap from components
    |   |
    |   |-- stylesheets
    |   |   |-- app.css
    |   |
    |   |-- .htaccess
    |   |-- 404.html
    |   |-- favicon.ico
    |   |-- index.html
    |   |-- robots.txt
    |
    |-- test (mocha)
    |   |-- ...
    |
    |-- .editorconfig
    |-- .gitattributes
    |-- .gitignore
    |-- .jshintrc
    |-- component.json
    |-- Gruntfile.js
    |-- package.json